reviews.text: Hidden on the 1/F of a new residential complex but with its own staircase and lift, is a large restaurant by HK standard.  About 5min walk from the nearest metro station.  Run by NGO and also used for training purposes, serves high CP value meals and also good for hang out as it is large and one can easily find your corner though some seats are quite close to each other.  As in the middle of a residential area, so even the window seats will not have much view except if one enjoys watching the market goers or passing-by from a distance.  Also can be booked for functions.
